## Project Setup (Once)

These are project-level infrastructure created once and referenced by every feature:

```
/vision → creates .specs/vision.md (app purpose, target users, tech stack)
    │
    ├──▶ /personas → creates .specs/personas/ (who uses this, who doesn't)
    │
    └──▶ /design-tokens → creates .specs/design-system/tokens.md
                          (reads vision + personas to derive personality + values)
```

All three are optional but improve every spec that follows. `/spec-first` will note what's missing and still work without them.

